@startuml UC03_sequence
title UC03 - Quen va dat lai mat khau
actor "Nguoi dung" as User
boundary "ForgotResetPage" as ForgotResetPage
control "AuthController" as AuthController
control "PasswordResetService" as PasswordResetService
control "EmailNotificationService" as EmailService
control "PasswordEncoder" as PasswordEncoder
database "UserRepository / users" as UserRepo
database "PasswordResetTokenRepository /\npassword_reset_tokens" as TokenRepo

User -> ForgotResetPage : Nhap email/username
User -> ForgotResetPage : Bam nut Gui ma reset
ForgotResetPage -> AuthController : POST /api/auth/forgot-password
AuthController -> PasswordResetService : forgotPassword(identifier)
PasswordResetService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase()\nor findByEmailIgnoreCase()
UserRepo --> PasswordResetService : User/null
alt Tai khoan ton tai
  PasswordResetService -> TokenRepo : save(tokenHash, expiresAt, usedAt=null)
  PasswordResetService -> EmailService : sendPasswordResetToken(user, rawToken)
  PasswordResetService --> AuthController : ForgotPasswordResponse
  AuthController --> ForgotResetPage : 200 + thong bao tao token
else Tai khoan khong ton tai
  PasswordResetService --> AuthController : Generic response (an toan)
  AuthController --> ForgotResetPage : 200 + thong bao chung
else Loi CSDL
  TokenRepo --> PasswordResetService : DataAccessException
  AuthController --> ForgotResetPage : 500 Loi he thong
end

User -> ForgotResetPage : Nhap token + mat khau moi
User -> ForgotResetPage : Bam nut Dat lai mat khau
ForgotResetPage -> AuthController : POST /api/auth/reset-password
AuthController -> PasswordResetService : resetPassword(token,newPassword)
PasswordResetService -> TokenRepo : findByTokenHash()
alt Token hop le va chua dung
  PasswordResetService -> PasswordEncoder : encode(newPassword)
  PasswordEncoder --> PasswordResetService : passwordHash
  PasswordResetService -> UserRepo : save(user.password)
  PasswordResetService -> TokenRepo : findByUserIdAndUsedAtIsNull()
  PasswordResetService -> TokenRepo : mark usedAt cho token
  PasswordResetService --> AuthController : MessageResponse success
  AuthController --> ForgotResetPage : 200 Dat lai thanh cong
else Token sai/het han/da dung or password moi khong hop le
  PasswordResetService --> AuthController : IllegalArgumentException
  AuthController --> ForgotResetPage : 400 + thong bao loi
else Loi CSDL
  TokenRepo --> PasswordResetService : DataAccessException
  AuthController --> ForgotResetPage : 500 Loi he thong
end
@enduml
